data.description: Christmas is here with a $5,000 price reduction and a seller concession of $5,000 for closing costs, buyer modifications, etc. to make this home yours before Christmas!  Nestled in the delightful neighborhood of Flint, just south of Tyler, this single-family home is a captivating blend of comfort and sophistication.  With impeccable features and a prime location, this property is a standout gem.  Inside, you'll find low-maintenance flooring that's not only stylish but also built to withstand the demands of daily life.  The living room is centered around a cozy bricked wood-burning fireplace, adding both warmth and character to your home.  The kitchen, designed with an open-concept in mind, features a spacious breakfast bar – an ideal spot for quick meals and entertaining.  Custom wood cabinets and stainless steel appliances make it a dream kitchen for any chef.  The master suite is a sanctuary, boasting an elegant tray ceiling that sets a serene and sophisticated tone.  The master bathroom is equally impressive, offering a relaxing soaking tub and a separate walk-in shower for your comfort.  With additional features such as a 20 x 30 storage building, built-in shelving in the garage, an open-concept floor plan, and the sense of community in this established neighborhood, this home offers an exceptional living experience. Don't let this opportunity pass you by.  It's ready for you to move in, start anew, and create cherished memories.  Schedule a viewing today to witness the beauty and comfort of this exceptional Flint residence.
